platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Build up a farm & grow veggies

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Gérez la ferme comme un pro

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Even a kid can run Dr. Panda’s farm, and ours love being in charge. Who wouldn’t? Milking cows, gathering honey, making jam—it’s easy to figure out and fun selling food to unlock new activities. Plus, the papercraft-style animals couldn’t be more adorable.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Grow wheat, collect milk, and make bread on your own farm.
La vie à la ferme, c’est pas de tout repos !
